## Multiple pairwise comparisons {.smaller}

Quick aside


::: {.cell output-location='slide'}

```{.r .cell-code}
# save statistical test result
pairwise <- bfam |>
  t_test(weight ~ family, ref.group = "B1")


ggboxplot(bfam, x = "family", y = "weight", fill = "weight", ) +
  stat_pvalue_manual(
    pairwise,
    label = "p.adj",
    y.position = c(30, 32, 34)
  ) +
  ylim(10, 38)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr}

```
